      {
        "type": "markdown",
        "embeddableConfig": {
          "content": "## RigSignal Overview\nYour gaming session history at a glance. Use this dashboard to check recent session health, compare which games you've played most, and confirm your hardware is being captured correctly. From here, drill into **[Game Performance](/app/dashboards#/view/rigsignal-game-perf)** for per-title FPS analysis, **[System Health](/app/dashboards#/view/rigsignal-system-health)** for thermal and hardware detail, **[Engine & Diagnostics](/app/dashboards#/view/rigsignal-engine)** for eBPF scheduler investigation, or **[Software Stack](/app/dashboards#/view/rigsignal-software)** for driver/Proton/network context.",
          "settings": {
            "open_links_in_new_tab": true
          }
        },
